title: Son of a Boy Dad: Ep. 78 - Ali Macofsky
description:
Son of a Boy Dad: Ep. 78 - Ali Macofsky -- Lil Sas & Rone are joined by Ali Macofsky: a hilarious stand-up comedian of KissFM, Kill Tony, Joe Rogan, & JFL New Faces fame -- We discuss NY vs. LA comedy, Australian dick appointments, kids with divorced parents, ADHD, Jean-Michel Basquiat, prank calls, subways, ubers, sex tapes, & more -- Full episode also available on YouTube, thanks for listening/watching!


You can find every episode of this show on Apple Podcasts, Spotify or YouTube. Prime Members can listen ad-free on Amazon Music. For more, visit barstool.link/sonofaboydad
